# Test Layout (Hard-Break)

- Never place tests under `src/**`.
- Forbidden in `src/**`: `*.test.*`, `*.bench.*`, `__tests__/`, `*.test-helper.*`.
- Place tests under `tests/**` only:
  - Unit: `tests/unit/**`
  - Integration: `tests/integration/**`
  - Helpers/fixtures: `tests/support/**` or `tests/fixtures/**`
- Mirror feature paths from `src/` to keep discoverability.

## Required when creating/moving tests

1. Keep production code in `src/**` test-free.
2. Update Vitest include globs to `tests/**/*.test.?(c|m)[jt]s?(x)`.
3. Keep coverage scope on `src/**` only.
